room_title: Escape room "The Haunted Escape" by Denver Escapes in Charlotte
room_description: It’s Halloween night and you and your friends are out trick or treating. As you begin to walk by the neighborhood recluse’s house you hear a loud scream and decide to investigate. As you and your friends enter the stranger’s house the door slams behind you locking you in. You and your friends must now find a way to escape before you are trapped forever!
